# Release Focus (v1.6.0) - Production ML/AI/Mobile Implementation

## Option B: Real Data Collection & Model Improvement ✅
- **BenchmarkCollector**: Live system metrics collection during gaming sessions (450 lines)
- **Hardware Detection**: psutil + GPUtil + nvidia-smi integration
- **Session Recording**: Start/stop recording with automatic benchmark archiving
- **ML Export Format**: Automatic conversion to training data format
- **ModelOptimizer**: GridSearchCV + RandomizedSearchCV hyperparameter tuning (469 lines)
- **Model Evaluation**: Confusion matrices, feature importance, cross-validation metrics

## Option C: Complete Mobile Companion App ✅
- **Production WebSocket Server**: FastAPI-based real-time server (405 lines)
- **Connection Manager**: Device lifecycle management with reconnection handling
- **QR Code Pairing**: Time-limited token-based secure pairing
- **React Native App**: Complete mobile UI with bottom tab navigation (850 lines)
- **Real-Time Dashboard**: Live CPU, GPU, RAM, power metrics with progress bars
- **Material Design**: react-native-paper integration with dark theme

## Option D: Complete RL Optimizer ✅
- **DQNAgent**: Production Deep Q-Network implementation (406 lines)
- **DQNetwork**: PyTorch neural network with layer normalization and dropout
- **ReplayBuffer**: Experience replay with named tuples for efficient sampling
- **Target Network**: Periodic updates for training stability
- **Epsilon-Greedy**: Exploration strategy with configurable decay
- **Gaming Environment**: Simulated environment for profile optimization

## Option E: Production Documentation ✅
- **USER_GUIDE.md**: Comprehensive user documentation (462 lines)
- **INSTALLATION_GUIDE.md**: Step-by-step installation for all platforms (397 lines)
- **FAQ.md**: 40+ questions covering all aspects (435 lines)
- **Gaming Profiles**: Detailed guides for Competitive, Balanced, Streaming modes
- **ML/AI Features**: Complete documentation for all AI capabilities

# Technical Achievements

## Machine Learning (v1.3.0)
- Random Forest Classifier: 100 estimators, 15 features, 4 profile classes
- Gradient Boosting Ensemble: Multi-output FPS/power/temp prediction
- Cross-validation: 5-fold CV with stratified sampling
- Feature engineering: Hardware specs + usage patterns → optimal profiles
- Model persistence: Pickle serialization with versioning

## Deep Learning (v1.4.0)
- **CNN Architecture**: 3 conv layers (128→256→512 filters) + batch norm + dropout
- **LSTM Architecture**: 2-layer bidirectional (256 hidden units) + attention
- **VAE Architecture**: Encoder-decoder with latent dim 4, reconstruction loss + KL
- **Training Features**: Early stopping, gradient clipping, learning rate scheduling
- **Production Ready**: Graceful fallbacks, comprehensive error handling

## Cloud API (v1.3.0)
- FastAPI: Async REST API with Pydantic validation
- 7 Endpoints: Health, profile recommend, performance predict, community submit/stats, profiles list
- CORS Middleware: Cross-origin request support
- Security Framework: HTTPBearer token authentication ready
- Scalability: Uvicorn ASGI server with worker process support

## Deployment Infrastructure (v1.5.0)
- Docker: Multi-stage builds with health checks
- Kubernetes: 3-replica deployment with autoscaling ready
- Persistent Storage: 10GB models + 50GB community data
- Load Balancing: Service mesh ready
- Monitoring: Prometheus-compatible metrics endpoints

